-build-a-tool-that-s-designed-to-make-learning-interactive", "title": "Hi, PH community! Helping build a tool that's designed to make learning interactive.", "descriptionPreview": "<p>Hi folks! <br>I'm Anisha, a growth strategist, and we're building AI-powered learning that actually adapts to each person. I started out editing content, but now I'm all about making interactive learning accessible to everyone (because, let's be real, we've all sat through terrible training videos). When I'm not nerding out over AI and growth automation, you'll find me on the golf course -- I'm a professional golfer ranked in India's top 30! Nothing like a morning round to spark the best ideas. Super passionate about using AI to democratize great education. <br>We're launching on Product Hunt soon, and I'd love to know: what's your biggest pain point when using AI to build decks, slides, training, or lessons?</p>", "featuredAt": null, "pinned": false, "user": {"id": "8787364", "name": "Anisha Agarwalla", "username": "anisha_agarwalla", "avatarUrl": "https://ph-avatars.imgix.net/8787364/6e8a84a0-4b52-4fb9-8631-259f9ef9159e.png", "__typename": "User", "isAccountVerified": true, "isAmbassador": false, "selectedBylineProduct": {"id": "1110946", "name": "Creatium", "slug": "creatium", "logoUuid": "7954cf82-59c8-40f6-8e98-1cc49c537f93.png", "isNoLongerOnline": false, "__typename": "Product"}, "topProductBadge": null, "topHunterBadge": null, "topLaunchBadge": null}, "hasVoted": false, "votesCount": 3, "__typename": "DiscussionThread", "commentsCount": 7, "featuredComment": null, "primaryForum": {"id": "483", "slug": "introduce-yourself", "subject": {"id": "68", "name": "Introduce yourself", "thumbnailUuid": "59c8a9ba-8cc1-4eae-945e-ef8f8ed2f383.svg", "__typename": "DiscussionCategory"}, "__typename": "DiscussionForumType"}}, "__typename": "DiscussionThreadEdge"}, {"node": {"id": "756243", "pageViewsCount": 239, "slug": "product-hunt-ai-coach", "createdAt": "2025-09-28T14:40:13-07:00", "path": "/p/creatium/product-hunt-ai-coach", "title": "Product Hunt AI Coach", "descriptionPreview": "<p>We made a product hunt AI coach! Do check it out... we named her Christina, in honor of @chrismessina who has given us great advice about product hunt! <br>Experience the product hunt coach at this link. We used our AI tool called Creatium to create interactive content on how to handle a product hunt campaign... check it out at the below link! If you do have feedback on the experience, you could provide it on our product hunt page... https://www.producthunt.com/prod... We very much appreciate your inputs and support. Thank you!<br>Launching on product hunt: interactive content with a coach</p><img src=\"https://ph-files.imgix.net/3c67c6ce-90f7-4bce-b302-d6ddd2264b2c.png?auto=compress&amp;codec=mozjpeg&amp;cs=strip&amp;auto=format\" style=\"max-width: 100%\"><p></p><p></p>", "featuredAt": null, "pinned": false, "user": {"id": "8973779", "name": "Deepak Sekar", "username": "drcreatium", "avatarUrl": "https://ph-avatars.imgix.net/8973779/f78e549d-5e41-44d2-a198-a517e4b62f5c.png", "__typename": "User", "isAccountVerified": false, "isAmbassador": false, "selectedBylineProduct": {"id": "1110946", "name": "Creatium", "slug": "creatium", "logoUuid": "7954cf82-59c8-40f6-8e98-1cc49c537f93.png", "isNoLongerOnline": false, "__typename": "Product"}, "topProductBadge": null, "topHunterBadge": null, "topLaunchBadge": null}, "hasVoted": false, "votesCount": 27, "__typename": "DiscussionThread", "commentsCount": 9, "featuredComment": null, "primaryForum": {"id": "531776", "slug": "creatium", "subject": {"id": "1110946", "name": "Creatium", "logoUuid": "7954cf82-59c8-40f6-8e98-1cc49c537f93.png", "__typename": "Product"}, "__typename": "DiscussionForumType"}}, "__typename": "DiscussionThreadEdge"}, {"node": {"id": "211477", "pageViewsCount": 78, "slug": "i-ve-spent-over-a-decade-in-b2b-sales-and-now-building-chatgpt-sales-super-app-ama", "createdAt": "2023-05-23T00:04:00-07:00", "path": "